feat: Add QtClockWidget and QtEffectWindowManager for enhanced backdrop effects
- Implemented QtClockWidget to display time with various backdrop effects (Acrylic, Blur, Mica, MicaAlt, Aero). - Created QtEffectWindowManager to manage multiple effect windows with grid layout and visibility monitoring. - Introduced QtEffectWindow for robust title bar support, allowing both pure Qt and Win32 implementations. - Unified Qt header management for compatibility across different Qt versions. - Added comprehensive README documentation detailing features, build instructions, usage, and troubleshooting. - Integrated qtacrylicmaterial for optimized background rendering.
